"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"ev82-ep1-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미사키","body":"나는 괜찮은데……\n항상 팝핀파 멤버들끼리 먹잖아?\n괜찮아?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"ev82-ep1-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"리미","body":"괜찮아! 미사키 짱도 친구이고\n아직 호러에 대한 이야기도 더 하고 싶은걸!\n괜찮지, 사아야 짱!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"ev82-ep1-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"사아야","body":"물론이야! 안뜰에서 기다릴 테니까\n도시락 가지고 와.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"ev82-ep1-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"코코로","body":"그러면 준비 다 됐으려나?\n모두 같이 가자! 잘 먹겠습니다~!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf_left01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"ev82-ep1-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미사키","body":"……왜 코코로가 지휘하는 걸까~?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"ev82-ep1-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"사아야","body":"코코로도 같은 반이니까\n미사키가 있다고 불렀어. 부르지 말걸 그랬나?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"ev82-ep1-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미사키","body":"아니, 상관없는데……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"ev82-ep1-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"카스미","body":"와앗!? 코코롱 도시락 맛있겠다!\n저기 있지, 이 계란말이랑 그 고기 바꾸지 않을래……?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"surprised01","exp